    | Organisations whose core activity is to improve social mobility (including all education and training providers) are not eligible if applying based on business-as-usual activities. As an enterprise award, it is focused on recognising social mobility initiatives that are
    strong class="govuk-!-font-weight-bold"
      |  discretionary or that are in partnership with businesses for whom it is discretionary.

